Hi there! Thanks for reaching out. The ad approval process usually takes between 1-2 business days, but sometimes it can be quicker. If your account is new and hasn't been verified yet, you might need to provide additional information for verification. You can email adsupport@newsbreak.com with the subject line: Business Verification and include your company's full address, legal entity name, EHID or DUNS number, primary contact person's name, and phone number. This will help expedite the review process. Let me know if you need further assistance!
